  5) User can open a drill-down to see underlying events and an explanation panel that shows how each narrative contributed to authority_weight and credibility_proxy, plus the proximity to the IPI score.
  6) Sandbox: User can open a sandbox modal or dedicated page to adjust weights (e.g., Narrative 50%, Credibility 35%, Risk 15%) and run simulations; the UI shows a list of simulated IPI results with scenario names and explanations, and a comparison chart (if implemented) that highlights score deltas across scenarios.
  7) All results render with the design system and style guidelines: premium fintech aesthetic, strong typographic hierarchy, accessible contrast, and clean data-forward visuals.

